casebody.data:
Tuesday, March 17, 1992

MERIT DOCKET

92-454. State, ex rel. Thrower, v. Beacon Journal Publishing Co.

In Mandamus. This cause originated in this court on the filing of a complaint for a writ of mandamus and was considered in a manner prescribed by law. Upon consideration thereof,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that said writ be, and the same is hereby, denied, effective March 13, 1992.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Douglas, Wright, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., concur.
